                </FooterDetails>
                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>The "Acronyms" web page contains a list of acronyms that are found on the CMS website, as well as other acronyms that are used frequently. An acronym is a term formed from the initial letter or letters of each of the major parts of a longer compound term.</Paragraph>
