                    <WebAddress>https://www.cms.gov/Medicare/Prescription-Drug-Coverage/LimitedIncomeandResources</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Low Income Subsidy</Header>
                <Paragraph>The "Limited Income and Resources" web page answers questions about the Low Income Subsidy (LIS). The LIS helps Medicare participants pay for prescription drugs, and it lowers the costs of Medicare prescription drug coverage.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
