                </FooterDetails>
                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>The Medicare Learning Network has published the booklet "Medicare Fraud and Abuse: Prevent, Detect, Report" The CMS posted the booklet on its website in Portable Document Format (PDF) for viewing and downloading.</Paragraph>
