                <Header>Regional Offices</Header>
                <Paragraph>Regional Offices are the State and local presence of the CMS. Regional field staff work with beneficiaries, healthcare providers, State governments, CMS contractors, community groups, and others, to educate and inform and to answer questions.</Paragraph>
